	<h1>Make an Entire List Item Clickable</h1>
	<p>The anchor tag in the categories list above is limited to the heading tag, but don't let that fool you: the enire list item is clickable. To find out how this technique is accomplished, <a href="../../index.html?p=501">read the original CSS Newbie article here.</a></p>
